    64→/// Builder for iteration feedback injected via `--append-system-prompt`.
    65→///
    66→/// Aggregates status, git changes, and signals from the prior iteration
    67→/// into a compact system prompt that gives Claude context about its progress.
    68→pub struct IterationFeedback {
